quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  2,6,"Ɓeen yedduɓe ngoonɗintaa foti a jeertinii ɓe wolla a jeertinaani, fof foti e mum en"
  2,7,"Alla muppi ɓerɗe maɓɓe, wirngallo woni noppi e gite maɓɓe lette mawɗe na woodani ɓe"
  2,8,"Na woodi heen yimɓe wi'ooɓe min ngoonɗinii Alla e ñalaande wattan, tawa ɓe ngoonɗinaani"
  2,9,"Eɓe koda Alla e goonɗinɓe ɓe, alaa mbo ɓe kodata sonaa ko'e maɓɓe tawa ɓe nganndaa"
  2,10,Ko ñawo woni e ɓerɗe Alla ɓeydani ɓe ñawu maa lette muusɗe njan e mum en sabu ko ɓe pennannoo
  2,11,So ɓe mbi'aama taa bonnee e lesdi ndi ɓe mbi'a minen ko min moƴƴinooɓe
  2,12,Ko kamɓe tigi ngoni bonnooɓe kono ɓe tinataa ɗum
  2,13,"So ɓe mbi'aama ngoonɗinee wano yimɓe ɓee ngoonɗiri, ɓe mbi'a mbela minen ngoonɗina wano ɗaayɓe ɓee ngoonɗiniri, kono ko kamɓe tigi ngoni ɗaayɓe kono ɓe nganndaa"
  2,14,"So tawii ɓe kawrii e goonɗinɓe ɓe mbi'a: min ngoonɗinii, so ɓe njeewdii e seyɗanooji maɓɓe ɗi ɓe mbi'a: minen ko onon min ngonndi min njalkitat tan"
  2,15,Alla jalkita ɓe O ɓeydana ɓe bewre ɓe ngona e wemmbere
  2,16,"Ko ɓeen ngoni soodirɓe peewal majjere njeeygu maɓɓe alaa tono, te ɓe peewaano"